'''''阔褶蛙'''''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Hylarana latouchii''}}）為[[Ranidae|赤蛙科]][[Hylarana|水蛙属]]的一種。 已往被歸類為''[[Rana_(genus)|蛙屬]]''。<ref name=frost/>该物种的模式产地在[[福建|福建]][[挂墩|挂墩]]。<ref name='id4991'/>

==分佈==
''阔褶蛙''可發現於[[中國|中國]]東部及南部、[[香港|香港]]及[[台灣|台灣]]。[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]分佈於[[江苏|江苏]]、[[浙江|浙江]]、[[安徽|安徽]]、[[福建|福建]]、[[江西|江西]]、[[湖南|湖南]]、[[广东|广东]]、[[广西|广西]]、[[贵州|贵州]]等地，來自台灣的個體，可能被視為與大陸為不同品種。<ref name=frost>{{cite web |url=http://research.amnh.org/vz/herpetology/amphibia/?action=names&taxon=Hylarana+latouchii |title=''Hylarana latouchii'' (Boulenger, 1899) |author=Frost, Darrel R. |year=2013 |work=Amphibian Species of the World 5.6, an Online Reference |publisher=American Museum of Natural History |accessdate=15 October 2013 |archive-date=2018-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181227181448/http://research.amnh.org/vz/herpetology/amphibia/?action=names&taxon=Hylarana+latouchii |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==生態==
天然棲息地包括亞熱帶或熱帶的潮濕低地與山地森林、河流、淡水沼澤、間歇性溼地、水池、池塘，露天開挖的臨時水池、灌溉土地、運河和溝渠。它不被[[IUCN|IUCN]]視為[[瀕危物種|瀕危物種]]。

==描述==
''阔褶蛙''是一種小型蛙類，體長可達{{convert|4|cm|abbr=on}}。<ref name=Lue>{{cite web |url=http://amphibia.biota.biodiv.tw/pages/416 |title=''Hylarana latouchii'' |author=Lue, Kuang-Yang |work=BiotaTaiwanica |publisher= |accessdate=15 December 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015214940/http://amphibia.biota.biodiv.tw/pages/416 |archive-date=2013-10-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>雄蛙體型較小，約({{convert|38|mm|abbr=on}})，雌蛙則為({{convert|47|mm|abbr=on}}).<ref>{{cite book |title=Atlas of Amphibians of China |last=Fei |first=L. |year=1999 |publisher=Henan Press of Science and Technology |location=Zhengzhou | language = zh |isbn=7-5349-1835-9 |page=174}}</ref>於台灣發現的個體，平均體型較大。分別為 {{convert|44|mm|abbr=on}} 及 {{convert|55|mm|abbr=on}}。''阔褶蛙''在台灣全年皆可繁殖。<ref>{{Cite journal| volume = 17| pages = 1–10| last = Huang| first = Wen-San| author2 = Yu-Shan Cheng| author3 = Hsin-Yi Tu| title = Reproductive patterns of two sympatric ranid frogs, ''Rana latouchii'' and ''R. sauteri'', with comments on anuran breeding seasons in Taiwan| journal = Collection and Research| year = 2004| url = http://web2.nmns.edu.tw/PubLib/Library/research/200412-1.pdf| access-date = 2018-12-27| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034801/http://web2.nmns.edu.tw/PubLib/Library/research/200412-1.pdf| dead-url = no}}</ref>

可從 ''阔褶蛙''的皮膚中，分離出一種[[Antimicrobial_peptides|抗菌肽]]。<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Wang | first1 = H. | last2 = Lu | first2 = Y. | last3 = Zhang | first3 = X. | last4 = Hu | first4 = Y. | last5 = Yu | first5 = H. | last6 = Liu | first6 = J. | last7 = Sun | first7 = J. | doi = 10.1016/j.peptides.2008.10.016 | title = The novel antimicrobial peptides from skin of Chinese broad-folded frog, Hylarana latouchii (Anura:Ranidae) | journal = Peptides | volume = 30 | issue = 2 | pages = 273–282 | year = 2009 | pmid =  19022312| pmc = }}</ref>

